    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――月ストがBIG4になってしばらくした頃",
      "startTime": 0,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 2066.6666667000004,
          "startTime": 2.0666666667
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_09_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_09_01-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "今日もお疲れ様。生放送にインタビュー、CM撮影\nまであって大忙しだったな。体調は大丈夫か？",
      "startTime": 6.5666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_09_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_09_01-ski001.m4a",
      "text": "大丈夫です。むしろ{user}さんこそ\n疲れた顔されてませんか？",
      "startTime": 14.7666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_09_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_09_01-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "う、鋭いな。今度の打ち合わせ用に資料を作っていたら\nつい熱が入って……気付けば日付が変わっていてな",
      "startTime": 22.3666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_09_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_09_01-ski002.m4a",
      "text": "私達のために、遅くまでありがとうございます\nでも、たまには自分の体も労わって下さいね",
      "startTime": 31.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_09_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_09_01-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "ありがとう。もうすぐ新曲のMV撮影もあるし\nお互い体調には気をつけていこう",
      "startTime": 39.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_09_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_09_01-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "だが、これだけ過密なスケジュールなのに\n沙季は普段とまるで変わらないな。本当に凄いよ",
      "startTime": 45.5333335876,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_09_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_09_01-ski003.m4a",
      "text": "私の場合、千紗の忙しさをそばで見ていたのが\n大きいですね。その分、覚悟は出来ていましたから",
      "startTime": 53.8666669209,
      "sfxList": []
    }
  ]
}